# 实验2：平方和计算

## 题目要求
已知a=3，b=5，求sum = a² + b²

## 程序代码
#include <stdio.h>

int main() {
    int a = 3, b = 5;
    int sum = a * a + b * b;
    printf("a = %d, b = %d\n", a, b);
    printf("sum = a² + b² = %d\n", sum);
    return 0;
}

运行结果

```
a = 3, b = 5
sum = a² + b² = 34

学习要点

· 变量定义和初始化
· 算术运算
· printf格式化输出


**02_数学运算/sum_calculation.c**：
#include <stdio.h>

int main() {
    int a = 3, b = 5;
    int sum = a * a + b * b;
    printf("a = %d, b = %d\n", a, b);
    printf("sum = a² + b² = %d\n", sum);
    return 0;
}
